title: Gorillaz - The Singles Collection (320)
description:
Features the Gorillaz singles released from 2001 to 2011, and includes two B-side remixes and Do Ya Thing/911/Rhinestone Eyes, 3 singles that were not included in the original version (Rhinestone Eyes was only included in the vinyl release.)
As an extra treat, I included a folder with about 50 official Gorillaz artwork and wallpapers! Enjoy!
